                        Your goal is to be better than yesterday. You are your greate competition.
                        <br>All you nees is to know what your goal is and be consistent everyday in chieving it!
                    </p>
                    <a href="" class="btn" style="padding:5px 10px; border-radius: 30px; background-color:black;color:white;">Explore Now  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-2">
                    <img src="~/imgs/giay/all-sports-banner.png">
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--end - banner -->
        </div>
    </div>
    @RenderBody()
